{"tid":1635060,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"返屯門手足小心","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:14:51.000Z","uid":30001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4f53b3393cc5ed5f7c55211cd58c24fd53a2f4","tid":1635060,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"啱啱經過屯公，去屯旦方向過左汀九橋近深井入口<br />\n十幾部狗車，同成隊防暴裝popo 企左出黎<br />\n可能係set RB 截查"},{"pid":"f6ecf322f93fd4b862c45e11a66b26d534ab2bfb","tid":1635060,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"92f616464157c8771cb909b8d879b6ff4d0ef10d","tid":1635060,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際戰線] 連登開左英文台！English Channel is LIVE now on LIHKG!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634824</a>"},{"pid":"7cfaa5d14d1bae5b59842315bba5169535481ed0","tid":1635060,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:43:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民撳爆總行 atm 換美金保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行call loan 然後支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"h